summary: Can we please have a sitcom of Bucky and Sam as roommates that get into all sorts of shenanigans. Where they literally hate each...
body: Can we please have a sitcom of Bucky and Sam as roommates that get into all sorts of shenanigans. Where they literally hate each other but help one another through hard times like when Bucky has nightmares or Sam starts thinking about Riley. And they prank each other and make fun of each other but they get really protective when someone else makes fun of either of them. And Sam likes to throw magnets at Bucky and Bucky just brings home all different kinds of birds asking Sam if he knows them. And they bicker about who does the laundry and who has to wash the dishes this time and just a bunch of very mundane things. And Steve and Natasha make appearances every now and then. But it’s pretty much about Sam and Bucky becoming the best of frenemies. Marvel get on this shit!

summary: I Can't Take This (All This Meaningless)
title: I Can't Take This (All This Meaningless)
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2RLOLiw

by Cbyrno521

“Why are you making such a big deal over this?!” Peter all but growls, wishing he hadn’t agreed to be trapped in such a small space with Tony.

“Because kid, I made a promise! So it would be in your best interest to listen to what I have to say.“

“You mean your best interest.”

Tony slams on the breaks, startling Peter. Cars honk behind him, but their complaints go unnoticed as he swerves to the side of the road, turning his head and shouting “What has gotten into you Peter?!”

“What do you care?” Peter asks, Anger simmering and on the verge of exploding.

“I care a lot. Now ‘fess up kiddo, or do I have to call May?”

The car gets quiet, the low rumble of the vehicle mixing with the labored breaths of its occupants. Tony is glaring at Peter, who reaches for the door handle.

“Go right ahead, won’t help anyway. Calling a dead person won’t magically get them to answer.”

blog.description: I am an artist who creates props, costumes and gowns inspired by comics, glam rock, wizards, elves, faries, grunge music and all manner of geeky things.  I post a lot of nerdy things, which at the moment is Bucky Barnes, Captain Amercia, Sebastian Stan, Loki, Marvel, Nature, Fashion, Cosplay and Husky Puppies.  I cosplay Bucky Barnes and make all of my own costumes and gear.  If you would like to see more you can visit my Etsy page here:  www.etsy.com/shop/ThePotionsMistressand my Facebook page here:  www.facebook.com/CarolDaturaArts
